{"tid":2414150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奴隸也有人做！國泰航空「閉環式」編更已運作：機組人員工作周期達49日","createTime":"2021-02-19T08:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T15:34:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"37609d4f53185f8126a3d973df5dfde8547aed59","tid":2414150,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fpZepam9e5FCZtAY39HdAQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/7turEUbvVGZjpTvLErEgFA--~B/aD02MDA7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/singtao.com.hk/b9c35be15325bde1f6962ea3f503b0be\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FfpZepam9e5FCZtAY39HdAQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7turEUbvVGZjpTvLErEgFA--~B%2FaD02MDA7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fsingtao.com.hk%2Fb9c35be15325bde1f6962ea3f503b0be&h=336beb67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】政府早前公布於2月20日起，進一步收緊機組人員豁免到港檢疫的安排。國泰航空早前表示因應措施，作自願性「閉環式」新編更安排，機組人員在連續工作21天完成飛行行程後，返港隔離檢疫14天，再休假14天。<br />\n<br />\n據消息指，「閉環式」工作安排已開始實施，所有自願參加計劃的機組人員在21日的工作期間，每次返港後都須留在國泰航空的逸泰居酒店隔離。在結束飛行行程後，機組人員需在港島太古城的香港東隅酒店接受自我隔離14天，結束後就可休息14天，包括7天醫學監察，整個工作周期需49日。<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空表示會盡力為機組人員提供合適的幫助，包括提供津貼等，希望盡可減低工作對於機組人員日常生活的影響。"},{"pid":"47a5afe7aaada54ac67a8ae7acf032ab257b1469","tid":2414150,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:02:36.000Z","msg":"仲做緊既空姐,<br />\n<br />\n係咪女奴嚟？"},{"pid":"e3f28a9565c40aeb37aa74cdb3677af0d922ae4f","tid":2414150,"uid":281401,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:07:30.000Z","msg":"睇CX Secret先好笑<br />\n成班奴隸叫人唔好埋怨，話大把人爭住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n癡撚線，唔知以為揾好撚多錢<br />\n明明閪工一份"},{"pid":"c77a85828724ea0d568144090d7f26c6327c51fc","tid":2414150,"uid":133086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:07:31.000Z","msg":"條女做空姐就仆街囉<br />\n砌14日要隔35日先有得再砌"},{"pid":"8ce29efda97ce24c097408b008c7acc30b6f2544","tid":2414150,"uid":7482,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c77a85828724ea0d568144090d7f26c6327c51fc","tid":2414150,"uid":133086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:07:31.000Z","msg":"條女做空姐就仆街囉<br />\n砌14日要隔35日先有得再砌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴線 <br />\n有成35日你去偷食 重要帶番屋都唔驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bc8227573f12f98d2d1b67cfffce729c4dab31","tid":2414150,"uid":225192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:04:22.000Z","msg":"飛21 放14+14<br />\n大把地盤佬番緊六日放一日<br />\n話自己好高人工<br />\n香港奴隸制好耐"},{"pid":"9e5a4697fe8e2eb4b56b0cda1f1bbbb6787814d7","tid":2414150,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:59:03.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a8c0008dd02b115a8e40c03a4114a357ec9808f9","tid":2414150,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c77a85828724ea0d568144090d7f26c6327c51fc","tid":2414150,"uid":133086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:07:31.000Z","msg":"條女做空姐就仆街囉<br />\n砌14日要隔35日先有得再砌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:33:45.000Z","msg":"AV 劇情"},{"pid":"7b9a72b8315100a0fd808bd45acb508e3928ba71","tid":2414150,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3f28a9565c40aeb37aa74cdb3677af0d922ae4f","tid":2414150,"uid":281401,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:07:30.000Z","msg":"睇CX Secret先好笑<br />\n成班奴隸叫人唔好埋怨，話大把人爭住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n癡撚線，唔知以為揾好撚多錢<br />\n明明閪工一份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:34:07.000Z","msg":"變咗 M女 PAGE"}]}